      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software (Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1) operates under a documented software quality plan with version control, change management, and periodic benchmark testing per 21 CFR Part 11 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 is used under a validated installation with IQ/OQ/PQ documentation. Version control enforced via enterprise PLM. Benchmark suite executed quarterly; all benchmarks passed for the solver configuration used in this study."
