      "rationale": "Validation constructs use identical hardware specification as the device submission. Test protocol is ASTM F1717 as required by COU. Two-laboratory design provides inter-laboratory reproducibility data. No extrapolation beyond validated geometry or loading mode required for the regulatory submission."
