    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single-offset-distance testing; risk accepted given COU restriction to standard ASTM F1717 configuration and medium model risk level. Quantitative validation metrics (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) satisfied for all three QoIs across N=11 experimental constructs at two independent laboratories. Model credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
